 uracil biosynthesis (or metabolism) and methionine degradation in eukaryotes?","body":"<p>Is there any way in which uracil biosynthesis or metabolism could help cell in degradation of toxic levels of methionine?<\/p>\n","question_id":3638,"tags":["biochemistry","metabolism"],"score":4,"down_vote_count":0,"is_answered":true,"view_count":460,"up_vote_count":4}]}